ol.li:
We evaluate the decibel formula with I = \alert{10^{-11}} to find
			\begin{aligned}[t]
			                 D \amp = 10 \log_{10}\left(\frac{\alert{10^{-11}}} {10^{-12}}\right)
			                 = 10 \log_{10} {10^1}\\ 
			                 \amp = 10(1) = 10 \text{ decibels}
			                 \end{aligned}
